negotiator.utility
Interface Evaluator

All Known Implementing Classes:
EvaluatorDiscrete, EvaluatorInteger, EvaluatorObjective, EvaluatorPrice, EvaluatorReal
public interface Evaluator

Author:
Dmytro? Evaluator is an object that translates discrete values into an evaluation value. The UtilitySpace attaches it to an issue. It is saved if you save the utility space, using the setXML functions.
